lt's the arrogance of money!

258
00:39:17,881 --> 00:39:19,678
We didn't go begging to them!

259
00:39:19,982 --> 00:39:22,952
- We are happy as we are!
- What's the fight about?

260
00:39:23,988 --> 00:39:26,752
Think about Chandni
and her happiness

261
00:39:27,458 --> 00:39:31,656
l am confident Rohit
will look after her.

262
00:39:32,131 --> 00:39:36,795
