but you and me!

290
00:42:14,377 --> 00:42:18,838
We'll have our
honeymoon in Switzerland.

291
00:42:20,985 --> 00:42:25,718
What's wrong? Where are you?

292
00:42:56,958 --> 00:43:00,155
l can spend my whole
life with your love.

293
00:43:04,667 --> 00:43:08,433
- Come here.
- Why?

294
00:43:08,905 --> 00:43:11,568
Come on. l feel like kissing you.

295
00:43:12,875 --> 00:43:16,175
- l couldn't hear.
- Don't ruin my romance!

296
00:43:17,114 --> 00:43:22,143
An old joke. A fat man wants
to make love to a pretty girl.

297
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:25,956
The girl says, if you can
catch me, you can love me.

298
00:43:38,538 --> 00:43:41,632
So fat man, won't you kiss me?

299
00:43:43,044 --> 00:43:44,442
