Okay. Hold this.

313
00:44:39,639 --> 00:44:44,736
- Let this be.
- For ice cream.

314
00:44:47,715 --> 00:44:51,378
Get lost! Wants real stuff
for threatening with a toy gun!

315
00:45:08,738 --> 00:45:10,639
May l taste it?

316
00:45:19,351 --> 00:45:24,880
- May l ...?
- No way!

317
00:45:25,323 --> 00:45:27,758
Had half of mine and
won't give hers!

318
00:45:28,061 --> 00:45:35,832
Dropped my ice cream!
Give me a bite!

319
00:45:37,370 --> 00:45:41,307
Tonight... yes or no?

320
00:45:41,608 --> 00:45:45,340
- No, no.
- Come on, say yes or no.

321
00:45:45,680 --> 00:45:50,548
- No mischief in this cold.
- What else can we do in the cold?

322
00:45:50,852 --> 00:45:53,116
lt's very cold today.

323
00:45:53,455 --> 00:45:57,688
We'll do one thing, go to
the hotel, l'll give you cognac.

324
