326
00:46:06,670 --> 00:46:11,540
- Cognac is not liquor?
- No, cognac is not liquor.

327
00:46:30,996 --> 00:46:34,865
- Good heavens! Cognac...
- ls not liquor.

328
00:46:35,068 --> 00:46:36,592
What else is it?

329
00:46:36,936 --> 00:46:41,840
Romance, love.

330
00:46:42,042 --> 00:46:47,208
Youth. lntoxication. Wow!

