- What are you doing?
- l was sleeping.

342
00:54:25,325 --> 00:54:29,990
- Give me a kiss.
- l'm sleeping now.

343
00:54:33,267 --> 00:54:35,736
No, l won't give.

344
00:54:38,139 --> 00:54:40,802
You woke me from a dream.

345
00:54:41,310 --> 00:54:43,072
Fast give me a kiss.

346
00:54:54,091 --> 00:54:56,787
Aunt has come!

347
00:54:58,095 --> 00:55:00,689
From where do these aunts land up!

348
00:55:36,204 --> 00:55:38,400
Where were you? You took
ages to come to the phone!

349
00:55:38,640 --> 00:55:41,632
- l was in the bathroom.
- What were you doing?

350
00:55:43,312 --> 00:55:47,340
- Please tell me.
- Having a bath! What else!

351
00:55:51,555 --> 00:55:53,283
What's the matter?

352
00:55:55,459 --> 00:55:59,555
l'm dripping with water!

353
00:56:22,789 --> 00:56:25,588
- What are you doing?
- Talking to you.

354
00:56:26,026 --> 00:56:28,085
What were you doing before that?

355
00:56:30,331 --> 00:56:33,425
Looking in the mirror.

356
00:56:33,902 --> 00:56:36,200
How did you find my Chandni?

357
00:56:37,138 --> 00:56:43,135
- l love myself today.
- And not me?

358
00:56:44,847 --> 00:56:48,375
Why don't you understand?
l love you.

359
00:56:49,151 --> 00:56:52,212
That is why l like myself.

360
00:56:57,228 --> 00:56:59,958
When you call me yours...

361
00:57:00,631 --> 00:57:03,759
l feel proud of myself.

362
00:57:26,660 --> 00:57:27,423
Now what is it?

363
00:57:28,729 --> 00:57:30,891
l want to meet you this evening.

364
00:57:33,568 --> 00:57:36,333
- But where?
- On the terrace of your house.

365
00:57:37,906 --> 00:57:40,535
- Our terrace?
- l'll wait for you.

366
00:57:41,344 --> 00:57:48,217
- All right. l'll come.
- But as my Chandni.

367
00:57:51,221 --> 00:57:54,589
- What do you mean?
- ln milky white clothes.

368
00:57:55,259 --> 00:57:56,625
From head to toe.

369
00:58:37,573 --> 00:58:38,630
Up here!

370
00:58:47,684 --> 00:58:48,742
You are mad!

371
00:59:00,365 --> 00:59:03,061
What are you doing? Are you mad?

372
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:07,034
This is my style.

373
00:59:08,040 --> 00:59:09,302
Careful.

374
00:59:17,284 --> 00:59:18,581
Come back please!

375
00:59:48,252 --> 00:59:50,584
Ramesh here.
Rohit met with an accident.

376
00:59:51,389 --> 00:59:53,949
While landing. He's in the hospital.

377
01:00:09,308 --> 01:00:10,640
What happened?

378
01:00:11,144 --> 01:00:14,137
Don't worry. Everything will be fine.

379
01:00:14,481 --> 01:00:16,574
- Where is he? Can l see him?
- Not yet.

380
01:00:16,950 --> 01:00:19,111
Not now? What do the doctors say?

381
01:00:19,387 --> 01:00:21,616
- Nothing can be said.
- What?

382
01:00:21,922 --> 01:00:26,758
- ls he very serious?
- He's being operated upon.

383
01:00:41,677 --> 01:00:44,943
Do you know how this
accident occurred?

384
01:00:45,282 --> 01:00:47,512
- How?
- Because of her!

385
01:00:48,485 --> 01:00:50,419
She is very fond of flowers.

386
01:00:50,921 --> 01:00:55,518
To pamper her Rohit bought
flowers from all over town.

387
01:00:55,927 --> 01:00:58,294
He was showering her with flowers
when this accident took place!

388
01:00:58,630 --> 01:01:02,396
This happened because of you!
What do you want from us?

389
01:01:02,668 --> 01:01:03,828
Why don't you go away from here?

390
01:01:05,504 --> 01:01:11,068
l can't leave before meeting
Rohit, without seeing him.

391
01:01:11,344 --> 01:01:15,873
No! You won't meet him or
see him! Go away from here!

392
01:01:16,383 --> 01:01:21,150
Just once mother.
Let me see him just once.

393
01:01:21,489 --> 01:01:25,550
Then l'll do as you say.

394
01:01:26,293 --> 01:01:29,024
Let me meet him just once.

395
01:01:29,798 --> 01:01:31,163
Rohit has gained consciousness!

396
01:01:48,118 --> 01:01:51,247
You looked gorgeous from that height.

397
01:02:04,270 --> 01:02:06,670
What's the matter?

398
01:02:13,813 --> 01:02:17,147
What's wrong? Tell me.

399
01:02:18,052 --> 01:02:21,351
My right arm and leg aren't moving.

400
01:02:27,930 --> 01:02:32,367
- What's wrong with me?
- Your right side is paralyzed.

401
01:02:35,305 --> 01:02:40,038
Will l be able to walk?

402
01:02:40,610 --> 01:02:43,739
Will l ever get well?

403
01:02:44,781 --> 01:02:50,584
Of course you will but you have to
use your determination and will power.

404
01:02:59,164 --> 01:03:00,860
You have to get well.

405
01:03:02,033 --> 01:03:04,628
God has saved you for me.

406
01:03:06,206 --> 01:03:10,142
Now your life is
a trust meant for me.

407
01:03:19,653 --> 01:03:23,954
Welcome home smiling face, dark hair.

408
01:03:25,995 --> 01:03:29,021
Take me to my room.

409
01:03:48,953 --> 01:03:52,481
One thing is for sure,
Rohit brought joy home.

410
01:03:54,259 --> 01:03:58,458
Tell you something? The nurses
in the hospital were very pretty.

411
01:03:58,898 --> 01:04:00,728
Had l stayed longer,
l would've had an affair.

412
01:04:01,501 --> 01:04:03,969
l was in a hurry to get back.

413
01:04:37,974 --> 01:04:40,807
Why did you become silent?

414
01:04:43,113 --> 01:04:45,912
Hearing voices from the past l feel..

415
01:04:46,384 --> 01:04:47,851
Time has stood still.

416
01:04:50,054 --> 01:04:52,522
Don't hold back time. Let it go on.

417
01:04:55,761 --> 01:04:57,626
Will those days ever return?

418
01:04:58,697 --> 01:05:01,427
Yes, those days will return.

419
01:05:01,934 --> 01:05:03,300
l have full faith.

420
01:05:05,505 --> 01:05:07,302
Your faith is my life.

421
01:05:10,410 --> 01:05:14,108
And your life is my life.

422
01:05:16,183 --> 01:05:19,620
Today if l ask you for something,
promise you won't turn me down.

423
01:05:21,056 --> 01:05:22,921
Do you expect me to refuse?

424
01:05:23,692 --> 01:05:25,684
Every word of yours is my promise.

425
01:05:29,932 --> 01:05:35,337
From now onwards whenever l open
my eyes, l should see you before me.

426
01:05:38,342 --> 01:05:41,834
Today onwards my morning
will begin with your smile.

427
01:05:44,948 --> 01:05:49,682
And night will set under
the darkness of your lashes.

428
01:06:00,934 --> 01:06:02,161
What are you doing here?

429
01:06:03,002 --> 01:06:07,099
Can't you see mummy?
She's making breakfast for Rohit.

430
01:06:07,374 --> 01:06:10,276
Are we no more that you will
make breakfast for my son?

431
01:06:12,413 --> 01:06:14,574
She's establishing her
rights before marriage.

432
01:06:15,149 --> 01:06:17,845
She comes here every morning.
She's really shameless!

433
01:06:18,220 --> 01:06:20,653
Not shameless, very clever.

434
01:06:21,190 --> 01:06:25,889
She thinks if she can win Rohit's
heart, all the wealth will be hers!

435
01:06:26,228 --> 01:06:27,560
Are you listening to us?

436
01:06:29,097 --> 01:06:33,194
She thinks she can pull us away
from Rohit by doing all this.

437
01:06:33,536 --> 01:06:38,873
The world will laugh, not yet
married but always around my son!

438
01:06:39,276 --> 01:06:43,337
Do whatever you want, you cannot
become the mistress of this house!

439
01:06:43,581 --> 01:06:44,844
Go away from here!

440
01:06:46,650 --> 01:06:48,346
Keep the tray back.

441
01:06:51,389 --> 01:06:53,449
Don't you dare step
in my kitchen again!

442
01:07:08,408 --> 01:07:10,809
Don't cry for every little thing.

443
01:07:11,212 --> 01:07:15,672
Your tears will dry up but
they won't appreciate them.

444
01:07:17,252 --> 01:07:20,689
You've lost so soon.
You have major battles to win.

445
01:07:21,623 --> 01:07:26,618
What do l do? Mother gets
angry at every thing.

446
01:07:27,596 --> 01:07:31,829
And Pooja always hated me.

447
01:07:33,103 --> 01:07:36,266
Actually they want you
to get fed up and leave.

448
01:07:38,142 --> 01:07:40,076
Don't they want Rohit to be happy?

449
01:07:40,478 --> 01:07:46,213
They do but they want him
to be happy in their choice.

450
01:07:46,785 --> 01:07:48,980
And you're not their choice.

451
01:07:50,789 --> 01:07:56,625
lf Rohit sees tears in
your eyes, he will break down.

452
01:07:58,798 --> 01:08:01,858
So bear everything, put up with it.

453
01:08:02,836 --> 01:08:05,828
Take everything with a smile.

454
01:08:07,207 --> 01:08:12,077
For Rohit if not yourself.
For his happiness.

455
01:08:13,181 --> 01:08:15,615
You are right.

456
