463
01:13:16,919 --> 01:13:19,650
- She's cast a spell on him!
- What are you saying?

464
01:13:20,023 --> 01:13:23,425
- Listen to what l have to say.
- Son, you are unwell.

465
01:13:23,761 --> 01:13:26,730
- You need complete rest.
