466
01:13:26,964 --> 01:13:28,829
l want peace in this house!

467
01:13:29,033 --> 01:13:31,524
-But what's her fault?
- You keep... - Daddy...!

468
01:13:33,171 --> 01:13:34,159
Unnecessarily Pooja...

469
01:13:34,371 --> 01:13:37,273
You must rest son.
Pooja take him in.

470
01:13:38,044 --> 01:13:40,204
No need. l'll go on my own.

471
01:13:48,287 --> 01:13:52,850
Listen to one thing carefully.
Rohit is my only son.

472
01:13:53,293 --> 01:13:55,785
l don't want to lose him
because of you.

473
01:13:57,431 --> 01:14:00,594
Very shameless girl! Standing here
after listening to all this!

474
01:14:00,834 --> 01:14:04,397
Please be quiet. This is enough!

475
01:14:07,876 --> 01:14:12,575
Now go home.
They won't let you live.

476
01:15:09,145 --> 01:15:11,978
Are you angry with me?

477
01:15:13,182 --> 01:15:14,480
No.

478
01:15:24,461 --> 01:15:27,863
l've brought something for you.
Shut your eyes.

479
01:15:28,833 --> 01:15:30,528
l'll put it in your mouth
and you must identify it.

480
01:15:31,035 --> 01:15:35,769
- Why shut my eyes?
- l won't give you chilies!

481
01:15:37,943 --> 01:15:39,035
Feed me like this.

482
01:15:42,648 --> 01:15:45,947
Don't you trust me?

483
01:15:46,719 --> 01:15:49,245
l don't trust myself.

484
01:15:51,224 --> 01:15:55,025
- You did till yesterday.
- There's a lot of difference today.

485
01:15:56,664 --> 01:16:00,725
- What difference?
- Yesterday was a dream.

486
01:16:01,436 --> 01:16:03,028
Today is real.

487
01:16:04,873 --> 01:16:08,206
Real, dream, yesterday, today...
l don't understand...

488
01:16:08,443 --> 01:16:11,880
Why don't you understand?
l'm not the man you loved!

489
01:16:12,180 --> 01:16:13,478
With whom you sang and danced!

490
01:16:15,051 --> 01:16:17,747
How long will l amuse myself
with memories of the past?

491
01:16:18,355 --> 01:16:21,552
Why are you being so emotional?

492
01:16:22,292 --> 01:16:26,228
Emotions are all l have now.

493
01:16:26,396 --> 01:16:30,731
Everything else is...
All the dreams have crashed.

494
01:16:32,972 --> 01:16:38,308
They haven't crashed.
Our dreams will come true.

495
01:16:38,777 --> 01:16:42,441
How? With this handicapped,
cripple, helpless Rohit?

496
01:16:43,949 --> 01:16:47,010
You can't use these words to
describe yourself when l'm here!

497
01:16:47,888 --> 01:16:52,086
lf you could revolt against your
parents and society for me...

498
01:16:52,459 --> 01:16:56,920
Then can't l become your legs?

499
01:17:00,668 --> 01:17:02,899
l'll be your better half in
the true sense of the word.

500
01:17:03,405 --> 01:17:07,705
l'll be your hope, your strength.

501
01:17:08,611 --> 01:17:09,941
Your belief.

502
01:17:10,546 --> 01:17:12,014
Why don't you try to understand?

503
01:23:10,314 --> 01:23:13,875
Who did all this?

504
01:23:14,918 --> 01:23:16,352
l did it.

505
01:23:19,090 --> 01:23:21,252
- You?
- Yes.

506
01:23:23,194 --> 01:23:27,427
l don't need the
memories attached to them.

507
01:23:28,467 --> 01:23:33,701
Don't say that. Our love is
tied by very delicate threads.

508
01:23:34,007 --> 01:23:36,999
That is pity not love.

509
01:23:37,877 --> 01:23:40,345
And l don't want to
live with anyone's pity.

510
01:23:41,449 --> 01:23:47,685
What is wrong with you?
What made you change in one night?

511
01:23:49,357 --> 01:23:52,088
There is no place for
your love in my life.

512
01:23:57,499 --> 01:23:59,559
lt's not so easy to erase love.

513
01:24:00,470 --> 01:24:03,906
l'm not lifeless
like these pictures!

514
01:24:04,474 --> 01:24:06,237
l'm a living girl.

515
01:24:06,876 --> 01:24:09,175
ln whose chest beats a heart.

516
01:24:09,747 --> 01:24:12,648
l have feelings, a brain that thinks!

517
01:24:15,019 --> 01:24:18,012
By removing the pictures,
the symbol of our love...

518
01:24:18,590 --> 01:24:24,324
You've white washed the walls but
put the color of hatred on our love!

519
01:24:24,963 --> 01:24:28,297
Those pictures reminded me of
the moments that l can't forget!

520
01:24:28,801 --> 01:24:31,635
Your beauty, your smile,
your youth makes fun of me!

521
01:24:32,239 --> 01:24:34,264
Your singing to
please me stinks of pity!

522
01:24:35,108 --> 01:24:36,803
You want me to be dependant on you.

523
01:24:37,177 --> 01:24:39,202
No! lt's better to die
than live like that!

524
01:24:43,317 --> 01:24:47,151
Don't say that.

525
01:24:49,324 --> 01:24:53,590
Your life is more precious to me
than anything in this world.

526
01:24:54,630 --> 01:25:01,901
l know today your heart is
filled with hatred not love.

527
01:25:04,507 --> 01:25:06,135
Yet l ask you one question.

528
01:25:07,078 --> 01:25:13,574
lf l was in your place and you
in mine, what would you have done?

529
01:25:29,836 --> 01:25:33,966
l would have left you much earlier.

530
01:25:57,433 --> 01:26:01,393
l feel sorry for your pettiness.

531
01:26:02,472 --> 01:26:06,169
You don't know the meaning of love.

532
01:26:08,246 --> 01:26:11,477
Love is a gift of God not charity!

533
01:26:12,383 --> 01:26:19,552
You're talking of the girl who
was your heartbeat, your breath!

534
01:26:20,659 --> 01:26:25,723
- Your love!
- What has that love given me?

535
01:26:26,999 --> 01:26:28,934
You got everything!

536
01:26:30,036 --> 01:26:31,731
Family, name, wealth!

537
01:26:32,038 --> 01:26:34,166
And l have got venom!

538
01:26:34,675 --> 01:26:36,643
Defamation! Restlessness!

539
01:26:37,378 --> 01:26:39,073
lt snatched away
the peace of my life!

540
01:26:39,347 --> 01:26:43,681
The girl you talk of made me a
cripple instead of giving me life!

541
01:26:45,353 --> 01:26:48,380
What? You too accuse me?

542
01:26:48,990 --> 01:26:52,085
l made you a cripple?

543
01:26:52,295 --> 01:26:55,162
Yes! Till yesterday only my
family and the world said this.

544
01:26:55,464 --> 01:26:59,195
But today even l say you
crippled me! ln body and spirit!

545
01:27:03,106 --> 01:27:09,137
All right. lf like your family
and the world, you too believe..

546
01:27:09,914 --> 01:27:13,611
That l crippled you.

547
01:27:15,153 --> 01:27:17,588
l have no right to live in this house.

548
01:27:17,923 --> 01:27:19,948
Nor any right on you.

549
01:27:21,694 --> 01:27:24,026
l'm taking your gift of love with me.

550
01:27:25,497 --> 01:27:29,059
You may live with hatred.

551
01:27:30,103 --> 01:27:33,470
l will live with my love.

